LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.All Righ: Taa a sennda, a woʼʼina koo boo a ɓeyda jannginillum banda ƴamugo gaɗuɗo ɗum.
LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.CC BY: A foti a senda, a woʼʼina koo boo a ɓeydana jannginillum--koo bee sippugo fuu--ta hokka gaɗuɗo ɗum jooɓaari.
LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.CC BY-NC: A foti woʼʼinngo bee ɓeydanngo jannginillum ɗuʼum amma banda sippugo. Jannginillum maaɗa boo hokkay binnduɗo ɗum jooɓaari nden boo ɗum wonay na jey sippugo.
A foti tepaago bee yeedugo jannginillum ta hokka binnduɗo ɗum jooɓaari. Amma a fotaayi a ɓeydana ɗum koo boo a sippa ɗum.
A foti woʼʼinngo bee ɓeydanngo jannginillum banda sippugo ɗum ta hokka binnduɗo ɗum jooɓaari nden boo a waɗana jannginillum maaɗa kesum ɗereeji dow bindol gootol bee artuɗo windi jannginillum.
LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.CC BY-ND: A foti fahin a huutinira jannginillum no nufina, koo bee sippugo fuu. Ammaa a fotaayi a woʼʼinaɗum boo doole a hokka binnduɗoɗum njooɓaari.
LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.CC BY-SA: A foti woʼʼingo bee ɓeydanngo jannginillum ɗuʼum koo bee sippugo fuu ta hokka binnduɗo ɗum njooɓaari nden boo a waɗana jannginillum maaɗa kesum ɗereeji dow binndol gootol bee binnduɗo ɗum. Kala jannginillum ɗum a woʼʼini fuu doole mara ɗereeji gooti.
LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.Public D: Jannginillum ɗuʼum e feesi bee ketenɗe anndaaɗe.ley kiitaaji gaɗuɗoɗum. A foti yeedugo, woʼʼinngo bee ɓeydanngo jannginillum koo bee siippugo fuu
LicenseDescriptionsForConsumers.Special: Jannginillum ɗuʼum e mari ɗereeji ketaaɗi sey a ƴewɗa marɗo ɗi a ƴamamo kiitaaji maaji bee no haani ɗi kuutiniree.
LicenseDescriptionsForCreators.All Right: A marini semmbe daga kiitaaji winndooɓe feereən potaayi senndugo, woʼʼinngo koo boo ɓeydanngo jannginillum maaɗa no ɓe giɗiri banda yerduye maaɗa.
LicenseDescriptionsForCreators.CC BY: Ɗereeji ɗiʼi accay himɓe ngeeda, mboʼʼina, bee ɓeydana jannginillum maaɗa ko bee sippugo fuu to ha e ɓe ngokkuma njooɓaari dow ko artuɗa gaɗuɗa. Ɗiiɗo ɗi ɓurɗi huutinireego nder ɗereeji kuuɗe jey koomoye. E ɗi yeloo anndineego masin bee huutinirgo kuujeeji marɗe ɗereeji.
LicenseDescriptionsForCreators.CC BY-NC: Ɗereeji ɗiʼi accay himɓe mboʼʼina, bee ɓeydana jannginillum maaɗa banda bee sippugo ɗum. Koo nde jannginillum maɓɓe kesum ngokkete njooɓaari nden boo ɗum sippataake. Wonanaayiɓe doole marugo ɗereeji dow binndol gootol
LicenseDescriptionsForCreators.CC BY-NC-: Ɗereeji ɗiʼi ɓurii marugo ketannɗe nder ɗereeji joweegoʼo ɗi kuuɗe jey koomoye. Ɗi accay himɓe teppo bee ngeeda jannginillum maaɗa bee luttuɓe to ha e ɓe ngokkuma njooɓaari ammaa ɓe potaayi waylutugo ɗum ko seɗɗa koo ɓe sippa ɗum.
Ɗereeji ɗiʼi accay himɓe mboʼʼina, bee ɓeydana jannginillum maaɗa banda bee sippugo ɗum. To ha e ɓe ngokkuma njooɓaari bee to ɗereeji janngillum maɓɓe kesum e ley binndi nannduɗi.
LicenseDescriptionsForCreators.CC BY-ND: Ɗereeji ɗiʼi accay feereʼen kuutinira jannginillum maaɗa no ɓe nufori koo bee sippugo fuu. Ammaa ɗum yeedataake nder woʼineego maajum, nden boo a hokketeema njooɓaari.
LicenseDescriptionsForCreators.CC BY-SA: Ɗereeji ɗiʼi accay himɓe ngeeda, mboʼʼina, bee ɓeydana jannginillum maaɗa ko bee sippugo fuu to ha e ɓe ngokkuma njooɓaari nden boo ɓe ngaɗanay jannginillum maɓɓe kesum ɗereeji ley binndol gootol. Ɗereeji ɗiʼi e ɓaddootiri bee ɗereeji maɓɓitiiɗi peesiiɗi. Kala jannginillum kesum fuu ley maaɗa maray ɗereeji gooti, nden kala senndoode fuu e foti sippe. "Wikipedia" ba ɗereeji ɗiʼi huutinirta. E ɗum yelani kuujeeji kuutinirooje jannginillum daga "Wikipedia" ko kuutiniroojum ɗereeji nannduɗi bee ɗiʼi.

PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriAboutP1: Kolibri waɗaama bee Foundation for Learning Equality, Inc. Ɗaɓɓutu habaru ɗo'o:
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriAboutP2: Kolibri e waawi huwugo bee kompiita feere-feere, koo to henndu kompiita walaa.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriAboutP3: Kolibri e woodi nder kompiitaaji ɗuɗɗi koo toye nder duuniyaaru. Kala marɗo kompiita bee Kolibri hakkilana Kolibri muuɗum.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriAboutP4: Dawrooɓe e poti kawta kuuje kolibri bee kuuɗe wuro kuuje kolibri mawgo. To ɗuʼum waɗi, dawrooɓe wuro kolibri mango maray yerduye dow kuuje wuro bote fuu daga wuro kuuje kolibri. Ɗum tepeteema fahin ha senndirɗum ɗum "Learning Equality" kuutinirta nden ɓe maray yerduye dow maajum hamɓe fuu.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriAboutP5: Ngam ɓeydanngo kuuɗe kolibri bee janginillum gonɗum ɗoʼɔ, "Learning Equality" jaɓay anndinooje kuutinillum to kolibri hawti e henndu. E ɗum laarani kuuje ba koɗolle IP ndaaranɗe senndirɗum, bee tinndinoore kompiita bana kuwinoojum kompiita bee wakkatiiji. Ɗum fahin jaɓay kuujeeji ko laarani bana lamba himɓe huutinirooɓe, bee gure bote, hitaande tanyarde bee sendidirgo gorko e debbo, bee jannginillum no anndira. E ɗum habda bee bawɗe maajum fuu bee banda hoosugo anndinooje huutinirooɓe kolibri nakkiiɗe.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriOwnersP1: Huwu bee Kolibri nder laawol ngol ngomnati moɗon yerdi. To an mari kompiita bee Kolibri, an woni aynoowo tinndinooje dow huutinirooɓe Kolibri.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriOwnersP2: Tokku laawol bonngol ngam aynugo tinndinooje dow huutinirooɓe Kolibri. Aynu kompiita bee Kolibri boɗɗum. Huutinir bee paltirgel semmbinngel, hesɗitin kompiita ma no haani.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriOwnersP3: Taa suɓi hawtugo kuuje wuro bote maaɗa bee kuuje wuro kolibri, a hokkii dawrooɓe kuuje wuro kolibri mango yerduye dow kuuje maaɗa. Nden boo a hokkii fahin huutinirooɓe senndirɗum "Learning Equalities" yerduye dow maaje.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriOwnersP4: Anndin huutinirooɓe to ngonnda. To woodi fitina bee desirɗum maɓɓe ɓe nodduma.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersL1: A sennda paltirgel ma, a acca koo moye nasta desirɗum ma, koo a waɗa goɗɗum feere a aynataa desirɗum ma
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersL2: Ɗum haɓdi nastugo desirɗum kuutiniroowo feere
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersL3: Ittugo, nyifugo koo wonnugo nder Kolibri ko aynata Kolibri
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersL4: Maɓɓugo koo wonnugo Kolibri bee haɗugo kuutiniroowo feere janngugo bee Kolibri
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersP1: Huutinir Kolibri deydey no ɓe ciryori. Ƴamu yerduye daadiraaɓe koo jannginooɓe ma.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersP2: Ngam andinngoma yimɓe feere mbaawi yi'ugo ko ngaɗuda bee tinndinoore dow maaɗa.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersP3: Noddu dawroowo Kolibri maaɗa ngam famtugo tinndinoore nde ɗum sigii dow ma nder Kolibri bee moye waawata yi'ugo tinndinoore nden. A ƴamay dawroowo noye ngaɗata ngam hesɗitingo koo wilugo tinndinoore nden. Ƴamumo taa yi'i goɗɗo feere nasti desirɗum ma.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersP5: Ta nder kolibri ba kuutiniroowo binndaaɗo, dawrooɓe bee jannginooɓe e wuro bote maaɗa e poti ngiʼa anndinooje bana innde maaɗa, innde kuutiniroowo, duuɓi maaɗa, hitaande danyarde, lamba heftilla, jannginillum ɗum ndaaruɗa bee no keɓuɗa e poodi. Waɗuɓe kolibri fahin e poti kuutinira anndinooje maaɗa bee ɓe ngeedaɗe bee waɗooɓe ko ɗum janngata ngam woʼʼinngo jannginillum janngooɓe feere feere bee ko be nufooji maɓɓe.
PrivacyInfoModal.kolibriUsersP6: Taa koɗo nder Kolibri, dawrooɓe bee jannginooɓe feere mbaawata yi'ugo jannginillum ɗum an bee hoɓɓe feere ndaari.
